snippet.title: The Sims 4 City Living: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Take your Sims to the city and explore everything it has to offer, from bustling action outside your door, to unique situations that come only with apartment living.

Learn more about this Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/16994
 
Fulfill your Sims’ dreams in the diverse city of San Myshuno, and discover new neighborhoods and festivals.  Experience the charm and challenges that come with your Sims’ first apartment, then work your way up the penthouse of your Sims’ dreams.

Video features “Stop Desire” performed by Tegan and Sara

#sims4 #cityliving
